{
  "text": "Let's set up stack configuration for different environments. We use Pulumi's config system to read environment-specific values. In the code, we read configuration values with defaults, allowing the same code to work across environments. We create separate pulumi.yaml files for each environment, pulumi.dev.yaml files for each environment, pulumi.dev.yaml for development, pulumi.staging.yaml for staging, and pulumi.prod.yaml for production. Each file is entitled to it's culture form.",
